title: Whitney Houston anwuola
sentences: Otu nwanyị olu ọma, onye Amerịka, a ma ama maka ịgụ egwu, bụ Whitney Houston, anwụọla
E butere ozu Whitney n’ime ụlọ oriri n’ọñụñụ Beverly Hilton
A ma Whitney ama maka olu ọma ya
Ọ gbara afọ 48 tupu ọnwụ egbuo ya
Tupu ọ nwụọ, ọ gara na mpaghara Hollywood ebe a na-eme mmemme nturu ugo Grammy
Grammy bụ otu n’ime mmemme ndị a na-eji etuwe ndị aka ha pụtara ihe n’ịkụ egwu ugo
A na-ekwu na a hụrụ Whiteney anya ịkpazụ n’ụbọchị Tọzdee mgbe ọ gụchara nwa obere egwu n’ebe ahụ a na-eme mmemme Grammy
A hụkwara ya anya ọzọ na mgbede Fraịdee ebe ya na ndị enyi ya na-enwe añụrị n’ụlọ oriri n’ọñụñụ Beverly Hilton
